{"tid":1771562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗香港前途，請各位手足一定要支持李斯特城！（含詳盡分析）","createTime":"2019-12-06T03:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T22:30:48.000Z","uid":154872,"like":188,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a36c462783d90126288da207dd07aa159afd898f","tid":1771562,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"小弟學風水術數已經有好十幾年，<br />\n<br />\n由上年開始利物浦嬴Ｒ聯開始，至本季英超開季到而家<br />\n<br />\n利物浦氣勢如虹咁耐，香港就輸足咁耐<br />\n<br />\n利物浦本身以火紅為主色，隊波踢法以進攻為主，基本上屬火<br />\n<br />\n而地理上又喺李斯特城上面，正正同中共一樣！<br />\n<br />\n李斯特城係藍色，五行屬水，同香港一樣，打法又以反擊為主（同香港人反抗不謀而合）<br />\n<br />\n所以話，香港要嬴，利物浦一定要輸，請各位務必要撐李城！"},{"pid":"57842a2ce91150ba3e19ee684990a8a09183b192","tid":1771562,"uid":219225,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"波台法師&gt;cctai法師<br />\n分析得頭頭是道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea5d0752eab89948eaa9ca5db929b9a115a1fa1","tid":1771562,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a611c60edf4e5f7770aeeff6ea04593422c9fa","tid":1771562,"uid":154872,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"57842a2ce91150ba3e19ee684990a8a09183b192","tid":1771562,"uid":219225,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"波台法師&gt;cctai法師<br />\n分析得頭頭是道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2806b89fa66e65b8d39531c0c894cf3ee485125","tid":1771562,"uid":154872,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"另加李城今季有新星蘇安祖表現突出<br />\n<br />\n佢同新Ｊｏｋｅｒ個樣98.61%似<br />\n<br />\n而位置係中堅，正正係反擊第一點<br />\n<br />\n真係巧合到你唔信！"},{"pid":"6dfbe5859994f3419fa0c7b358cbc636aedfed85","tid":1771562,"u